40|$|The aim of {{this thesis}} is to analyze the {{personnel}} work in a concrete <b>small</b> <b>firm</b> {{in the field of}} engineering that deals with the reconstruction of the flats, core housing, renovation of bathrooms and kitchens. The work is divided into two parts [...] theoretical and practical. The first part compares theoretical with applied procedures. The practical part characterizes a <b>small</b> <b>firm</b> XYZ. In this part {{the strengths and weaknesses of}} personnel activities in a <b>small</b> <b>firm</b> are described and measures to improve the current situation are proposed...|$|R
